---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Free Medical Bill Decoder Tools" description="Decode confusing medical bills, generate dispute letters, and check for billing errors — all free. Fight back against overcharges.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F7B8C 0%, #2D4A7A 100%);" class="text-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        AI-Powered Medical Bill Tools — Free
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-bold mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-size: 48px;">
        Stop Overpaying for<br />Medical Care
      </h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
        Americans overpay billions in medical bills every year due to errors and confusing EOBs. Our free tools help you understand, dispute, and reduce your bills.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/eob-decoder" class="bg-white text-[#2D4A7A] font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors" style="font-size: 16px;">
          Decode Your EOB Free
        </a>
        <a href="/billing-errors" class="border-2 border-white/50 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors" style="font-size: 16px;">
          Check for Errors
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats bar -->
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-[#E2E8F0] py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-[#0F7B8C]" style="font-size: 36px;">80%</div>
        <div class="text-[#64748B] mt-1 text-sm">of medical bills contain errors</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-[#0F7B8C]" style="font-size: 36px;">$1,000+</div>
        <div class="text-[#64748B] mt-1 text-sm">average overcharge per hospital stay</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-[#0F7B8C]" style="font-size: 36px;">Free</div>
        <div class="text-[#64748B] mt-1 text-sm">tools to fight back</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tool Cards -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-center mb-4 text-[#1A2332]" style="font-size: 28px;">Three Powerful Free Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-[#64748B] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Start decoding your medical bills in minutes. No signup required for basic access.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- EOB Decoder -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#E2E8F0] p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #D0EFF3;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0F7B8C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A2332] mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">EOB Decoder</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748B] mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">Paste your Explanation of Benefits and get a plain-English breakdown of what you actually owe — and why.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-[#64748B] space-y-2 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> Identifies confusing line items</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> Flags potential overcharges</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> 3 free decodes per day</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/eob-decoder" class="block w-full text-white text-center font-semibold py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors" style="background-color: #2D4A7A; font-size: 15px;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#243D66'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#2D4A7A'">
            Decode My EOB →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Dispute Letter -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#E2E8F0] p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #EDE9FE;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A2332] mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Dispute Letter Generator</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748B] mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">Generate a professional dispute letter in seconds. Just fill in 5 fields and get a ready-to-send letter.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-[#64748B] space-y-2 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> All 50 US states supported</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> Professional legal language</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> 1 free letter per session</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/dispute-letter" class="block w-full bg-purple-700 text-white text-center font-semibold py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-purple-800 transition-colors" style="font-size: 15px;">
            Generate Letter →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Billing Errors -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#E2E8F0] p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #DCFCE7;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A2332] mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Billing Error Checklist</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748B] mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">Run through 15 common billing errors. Check each one against your bill to catch overcharges quickly.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-[#64748B] space-y-2 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> 15 proven error patterns</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> Interactive checklist</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#16A34A] font-bold">✓</span> Completely free</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/billing-errors" class="block w-full text-white text-center font-semibold py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors" style="background-color: #16A34A; font-size: 15px;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#15803D'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#16A34A'">
            Check My Bill →
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stripe CTA — amber for urgency -->
  <section id="complete-kit" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D4A7A 0%, #1A2D4A 100%);" class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-4" style="font-size: 28px;">Get the Complete Dispute Kit</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200 mb-8" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Unlock up to 20 EOB decodes per day, up to 20 letters, customizable letter templates, state-specific dispute guides, and step-by-step appeal instructions — all for a one-time fee.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="/api/create-checkout" class="font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors text-[#1A2332]" style="background-color: #E8A020; font-size: 16px;"
          onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#D4901A'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#E8A020'">
          Get Notified at Launch →
        </a>
        <span class="text-blue-300 text-sm">One-time payment. No subscription.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
